            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". This is true pretty much everywhere, including the United States, with all kinds of wild scenarios of thieves breaking into people’s garages, prying open sunroofs, and swiping vehicles from dealerships at night. Now, Atlanta Police Department is shedding some light on these crimes with a new video showing off a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
